fullplot: Two guys, Nick and Shawn decide a two week stint at a Cheerleaders' Camp is the perfect opportunity to score tons of meaningless romantic liaisons with lonely girls in tight-tops and short-short skirts. But their lusty plan to caress as many pom-poms as possible goes awry when one of the dudes fall in love.
plot: The two most popular guys in high school decide to ditch football camp for cheerleader camp. For the girls and for the glory.
title: Fired Up!

tomatoes.consensus: Though not as raunchy or juvenile as the average teen comedy, Fired Up is also not as funny.
